    <item>
      <title>特朗普特别顾问 2020 年选举报告的关键要点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/key-takeaways-from-trump-special-counsel-2020-election-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前特别检察官杰克·史密斯 (Jack Smith) 为针对当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的指控进行了有力的辩护，指控他参与了“前所未有的犯罪行为，以推翻 2020 年大选的合法结果”。以下是关键要点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/key-takeaways-from-trump-special-counsel-2020-election-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 17:43:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国接近达成查戈斯协议，预付 7 年费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/uk-closes-in-on-chagos-deal-with-7-years-of-payments-up-front</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为将查戈斯群岛主权割让给毛里求斯的一项优惠协议的一部分，英国愿意预先支付前七年的年度付款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/uk-closes-in-on-chagos-deal-with-7-years-of-payments-up-front</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 17:36:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>曼哈顿破败巴士枢纽获 19 亿美元贷款改造</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/run-down-nyc-bus-hub-wins-1-9-billion-loan-before-trump-return</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普就职典礼前几天，纽约市破旧的公交总站获得了联邦政府 100 亿美元改造资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/run-down-nyc-bus-hub-wins-1-9-billion-loan-before-trump-return</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 17:23:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Thune 计划利用快速通道法案实现能源“主导地位”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/thune-plans-to-use-fast-track-bill-to-achieve-energy-dominance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院多数党领袖约翰·图恩表示，他计划利用新共和党多数派制定的快速预算法案来扩大石油和天然气产量，实现美国的“能源主导地位”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/thune-plans-to-use-fast-track-bill-to-achieve-energy-dominance</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 16:57:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普提议设立“税务局”负责征收关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/trump-says-he-ll-create-external-revenue-service-for-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他将成立一个“美国国家税务局”，负责征收外国进口产品的关税，这一最新迹象表明，这位共和党人打算履行其连任后全面征收贸易税的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/trump-says-he-ll-create-external-revenue-service-for-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 16:51:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥将称中国通过欺骗手段取得超级大国地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/rubio-set-to-say-china-has-cheated-its-way-to-superpower-status</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议员马尔科·卢比奥将在周三的国务卿任命听证会上发表讲话，表示中国通过谎言和欺骗获得了超级大国的地位，而牺牲了美国的利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/rubio-set-to-say-china-has-cheated-its-way-to-superpower-status</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 16:50:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前不列颠哥伦比亚省省长退出 加拿大自由党领袖竞选竞争加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/canada-liberal-leader-race-narrows-as-ex-bc-premier-drops-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前不列颠哥伦比亚省省长克里斯蒂·克拉克（Christy Clark）放弃竞选贾斯汀·特鲁多（Justin Trudeau）的继任者，这进一步缩小了加拿大下一任自由党领袖和总理的选择范围。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/canada-liberal-leader-race-narrows-as-ex-bc-premier-drops-out</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 16:43:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥的 Sheinbaum 表示特朗普没有邀请她参加就职典礼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/mexico-s-sheinbaum-says-trump-hasn-t-invited-her-to-inauguration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥的克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆表示，她还没有收到唐纳德·特朗普就职典礼的邀请，并坚称这不是问题，尽管新任美国总统的关税威胁使他们的关系变得紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/mexico-s-sheinbaum-says-trump-hasn-t-invited-her-to-inauguration</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 16:42:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟主要大国呼吁紧急审查对叙利亚的制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/leading-eu-powers-call-for-urgent-review-of-sanctions-on-syria</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟主要成员国希望暂停对叙利亚的一些制裁，以帮助确保前总统巴沙尔·阿萨德倒台后权力的和平过渡，并使流离失所者能够返回家园。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/leading-eu-powers-call-for-urgent-review-of-sanctions-on-syria</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 16:35:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赫格塞斯称他将成为五角大楼的“变革推动者”，在确认听证会上反驳批评者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/hegseth-says-he-d-be-pentagon-change-agent-rebuffing-his-critics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普选定的国防部长人选皮特·赫格塞斯将自己缺乏高层管理经验视为一种优势，并在任命听证会上表示，自己将成为“变革推动者”，以“恢复战士精神”，并且“对某些公司、特定项目或已获批准的论述没有既得利益”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/hegseth-says-he-d-be-pentagon-change-agent-rebuffing-his-critics</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 12:22:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
